OL,3,CConsumer confidence rising as summer
OL,4,Choliday season begins
OL,6,FThe majority of UK households are
OL,7,Ffeeling financially secure, with 70%
OL,8,Fof people confident enough to plan a
OL,9,Fsummer holiday, according to a survey.
OL,11,FThe number of people feeling
OL,12,Ffinancially secure has risen this
OL,13,Fquarter by three percentage points to
OL,14,F58%, while confidence that the UK
OL,15,Feconomy is improving has risen to 17%
OL,16,Ffrom one in 10 three months ago, the
OL,17,FKPMG Consumer Pulse poll found.
