OL,3,CConsumer confidence rising as summer
OL,4,Choliday season begins
OL,6,FAround a quarter (23%) said they had
OL,7,Fbought more promotional or discounted
OL,8,Fitems when shopping, while just over a
OL,9,Ffifth (22%) said they used their
OL,10,Floyalty cards more.
OL,12,FOf the 70% who are planning a holiday,
OL,13,F34% say it will be in the UK, 21% are
OL,14,Fheading abroad and 15% are doing both.
OL,16,FHowever 75% of those going on holiday
OL,17,Fare taking steps to reduce the cost of
OL,18,Ftravel, such as going for fewer
OL,19,Fnights, self-catering or using a lower-
OL,20,Fcost airline.
