OL,3,CConsumer confidence rising as summer
OL,4,Choliday season begins
OL,6,FSome 33% say they will be taking
OL,7,Fchildren on holiday during term-time
OL,8,Fto cut costs, while one in five (20%)
OL,9,Fsaid their whole holiday would be
OL,10,Ftaken during term-time.
OL,12,FDespite the quarterly improvement in
OL,13,Feconomic confidence, half of people
OL,14,F(51%) feel that the economy is still
OL,15,Fworsening ` although this is down from
OL,16,F58% in the previous quarter.
